Channel5Plus1.uk.title: Peppa Pig

Channel5Plus1.uk.title: New: Candy Coated Christmas

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Robotic Manipulation: Penny tags along to Sheldon's first date with a woman he's been texting for months. Howard finds a new use for a robotic arm. (S4 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Boy-Scoutz 'n the Hood: During an all-syrup Squishee bender, Bart joins the junior campers, and ends up taking the embarrassing - and dangerous - Homer on a river rafting trip. (S5 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Last Temptation of Homer: Homer falls for his beautiful new colleague Mindy Simmons (guest star Michelle Pfeiffer), who shares his love of doughnuts... (S5 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mercedes and Ste find themselves on a path of self-destruction while the McQueens support Sienna - but drama soon follows...

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Animal Control
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Bulls and Potbellies: US sitcom. Frank and Emily make a breakthrough in their case. Shred bonds with Rick. And Victoria and Patel's father accidentally kiss... (S2 Ep8/9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sonia Dara: The remaining contestants learn that fame is a double-edged sword during an afternoon with fans of the show, before a group shoot where everyone gets covered in mud. (S16 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers have been watching Michael McIntyre's The Wheel, Jamie's 1 Wonders, Top Gear, Guillermo del Toro's Cabinet of Curiosities, and Wild Croc Territory. (S20 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics watch: I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here!, Hollyoaks, Stanley Tucci: Searching for Italy, Queens for the Night, and University Challenge. (S20 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Painter and lawyer Josh courts student and waiter Sophia. Leslie and Babs bond over their mutual admiration for Michelle Obama. Property developer Amanda meets sales exec Brad. (S9 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Spoiler Alert Segmentation: After Sheldon and Leonard have a row, Leonard attempts to move in with Penny, even though she isn't ready for such a big step. (S6 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tangible Affection Proof: Annoyed at being forced to celebrate Valentine's Day when he hates it, Sheldon delegates the task of buying Amy's gift to his assistant. (S6 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers have been watching Michael McIntyre's The Wheel, Jamie's 1 Wonders, Top Gear, Guillermo del Toro's Cabinet of Curiosities, and Wild Croc Territory. (S20 Ep9) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge on the Lam: Marge and her new friend Ruth Powers set off on a Thelma and Louise-style adventure, with Chief Wiggum and Homer in hot pursuit... (S5 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dolomite, Apple Slices, and a Mystery Woman: Sheldon makes a new friend, while Mary and George disagree on how to handle Sheldon's blossoming social life. (S1 Ep15/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Killer Asteroids, Oklahoma, and a Frizzy Hair Machine: A disappointing lack of success in a science fair competition sends Sheldon's life in a new direction. (S1 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Moving Day: Claire and Phil aren't convinced that Haley and Dylan can make it on their own when they move them into their new apartment before the baby arrives. (S10 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Ring: Beverly is furious when she discovers that her engagement ring is the same one that Murray gave to his former fiance. (S1 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Who Are You Going to Telephone?: Adam abandons Pops at Halloween to go trick-or-treating with a group of cool new friends who are really up to no good. (S1 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Remodel: After months of crashing with Malcolm and Marty, Calvin and Tina finally reveal the impressive results of their major home renovation. (S4 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Man Code: Calvin discovers that his friend Lorenzo is harbouring a secret. Should he tell Tina? (S4 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to Bro Money, Bro Problems: Calvin's wealthy and impulsive brother Curtis makes a surprise visit, creating chaos in the Butlers' lives. (S4 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Royal Visit: When Haley's astrophysicist boyfriend visits, Claire and Phil compete to prove who's smarter. Mitch and Cam go to a yoga retreat. (S9 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Daddy Issues: Gloria's ex-boyfriend Jorge's resemblance to Manny makes Jay question if he might be Manny's real dad. Phil agonises over getting an anniversary gift for Claire. (S9 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister, Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sports of the lawnmower, motorbike and bicycle variety.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Peter's: Gordon visits Peter's Italian Restaurant in New York, where the peace of Long Island is shattered by the antics of the volatile Pellegrino family who run the place. (S1 Ep1) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mixing Bowl: Bijou New York diner The Mixing Bowl is haemorrhaging money thanks to manager Mike's out of control marketing plans. Can Gordon get things back on track? (S1 Ep2) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dangers on a Train: While she's browsing for wedding anniversary cakes, Marge stumbles across a website for married people who want to have affairs. (S24 Ep22/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Heartbreak Hotel: Homer and Marge go on a big reality TV competition but are eliminated immediately. And the blame game starts soon after... (S30 Ep2/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Conjugal Conjecture: The gang face an awkward morning after Sheldon's mother and Leonard's father share an evening together. Penny's family arrive in town. (S10 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Military Miniaturization: Howard has a meeting with Air Force representative Colonel Williams about the gyroscope he invented with Leonard and Sheldon. (S10 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cold: Phil must get rid of some incriminating footage on Mitch and Cam's wedding video. (S6 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marco Polo: The Dunphys move into a cramped hotel room while their house is getting treated for mould. (S6 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Creepy Candy Coating Corollary: Due to a childhood snub, Sheldon is irked when Star Trek actor Wil Wheaton (guest starring as himself) takes part in the same contest as him. (S3 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cornhusker Vortex: Sheldon teaches Leonard about American football so that he can try to fit in with Penny's friends. And Raj and Sheldon have a kite-fighting contest. (S3 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Guitarist Amplification: Sheldon is annoyed when Leonard and Penny argue about Penny's male friend staying over and he has to act as peacemaker. (S3 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Adhesive Duck Deficiency: Leonard, Raj and Howard go on a camping trip that alters their minds. Penny dislocates her shoulder when she slips in the shower. (S3 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ju-Jitsu, Bubble Wrap, and Yoo-Hoo: When Sheldon is bullied by an unlikely character, Mary and George disagree about how to handle the situation. (S1 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Mother, a Child, and a Blue Man's Backside: When Mary bans Sheldon from reading a comic book, he decides it's time to stop living under his mother's thumb. (S1 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Clown Stays in the Picture: Krusty reveals the story of the lost film that he made in the 80s with Homer and Marge. (S30 Ep14/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: 101 Mitigations: Homer steals Comic Book Guy's car. Can he avoid a jail sentence? (S30 Ep15/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cruciferous Vegetable Amplification: Sheldon realises that he won't live long enough to download his consciousness into a robot body, so he tries to extend his lifespan. (S4 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Zazzy Substitution: The guys are concerned when a heartbroken Sheldon starts bulk buying cats after he breaks up with Amy, so Leonard tries to get Sheldon's mother to visit. (S4 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hot Troll Deviation: An embarrassing secret of Howard's comes to light as he tries to win back Bernadette. Sheldon and Raj have trouble working together. (S4 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Desperation Emanation: Leonard realises he's the only one of the gang with no girlfriend. Sheldon wants to get rid of his when she hatches a plan for him to meet her mother. (S4 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: $pringfield (or How I Learned to Stop Worrying and Love Legalized Gambling): Homer gets a job at Mr Burns' new casino and Marge gets addicted to the slot machines. (S5 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer the Vigilante: Homer sets up a chaotic vigilante group to combat one-man crime spree Molloy (guest star Sam Neill). (S5 Ep11/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Let's Go Fly a Coot: Bart develops a crush on Milhouse's Dutch cousin. And the family learn about Grampa's days in the Air Force. (S26 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Animal Control
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Beagles and Lemurs: US sitcom. Frank's investigation reaches a thrilling conclusion. Emily realises that she still has feelings for Shred. Series finale. (S2 Ep9/9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Eric Daman: With a rift between the remaining contestants ripped wide open, a shoot to win a car is followed by one of the most explosive panels ever. (S16 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the box this time: I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here!, The Great British Bake Off, The Crown, Family Fortunes, Love Is Blind, Mammals and This Morning. (S20 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Business development manager Emily and part-time model Matt look like a good match, until talk turns to aliens... And 73-year-old Michael's roaming eye gets him into trouble. (S9 Ep8)

Film4.uk.title: Free Guy
Film4.uk.description: (2021) Comedy action starring Ryan Reynolds. Guy lives in Free City. Free City isn't real. Nor is Guy. It's all a big online game. Can he take down the corrupt game publisher?

Film4.uk.title: Salt
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Action-thriller starring Angelina Jolie. A CIA agent goes on the run after a Russian defector claims that she's a sleeper agent who's about to commit a terrible act of terrorism.

Film4.uk.title: My Friend Dahmer
Film4.uk.description: (2017) Ross Lynch portrays serial killer Jeffrey Dahmer at high school in this biographical drama based on John 'Derf' Backderf's graphic novel.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Payroll
Film4.uk.description: (1961) British crime thriller starring Billie Whitelaw. When Jackie's husband - an armoured van driver - is killed in a heist, she vows to unmask those responsible and take her revenge.

Film4.uk.title: A Kid for Two Farthings
Film4.uk.description: (1955) Carol Reed's charming film stars Jonathan Ashmore as a young, impressionable boy who mistakes a one-horned goat for a unicorn in London's colourful Petticoat Lane market.

Film4.uk.title: The Man Between
Film4.uk.description: (1953) Atmospheric thriller set in post-war Berlin, where Ivo Kern (James Mason) and Susanne Mallison (Claire Bloom) get caught up in a maelstrom of bigamy, blackmail and bullets.

Film4.uk.title: Two Way Stretch
Film4.uk.description: (1960) Comedy. Peter Sellers, Bernard Cribbins and David Lodge star as criminals happily incarcerated in a prison run like a home-from-home for old lags and rascals by a liberal governor.

Film4.uk.title: Central Intelligence
Film4.uk.description: (2016) Action-comedy with Dwayne Johnson and Kevin Hart. Two former school buddies team up to thwart a terrorist plot. But things may not be as they seem. With Amy Ryan and Jason Bateman.

Film4.uk.title: S.W.A.T.
Film4.uk.description: (2003) Action with Colin Farrell and Samuel L Jackson. A loose canon joins an elite force to escort a fugitive to chokey. But the baddie's put a reward out for help with his escape.

Film4.uk.title: The Long Good Friday
Film4.uk.description: (1980) Bob Hoskins and Helen Mirren star in John MacKenzie's East London gangster thriller. Gang leader Hoskins' hold over his empire is under threat.

Film4.uk.title: Chopper
Film4.uk.description: (2000) Darkly comic, quasi-true crime biopic starring Eric Bana as notorious Australian criminal Mark 'Chopper' Read who, among other things, got a fellow inmate to chop off his ears.

Film4.uk.title: Picnic
Film4.uk.description: (1955) William Holden and Kim Novak star in this sweltering tale of deception, betrayal and illicit love in small-town Kansas.

Film4.uk.title: Arizona Raiders
Film4.uk.description: (1965) William Whitney's brutal western. Two former Confederate rebels are offered their freedom if they can track, catch or even kill their former gang mates. Starring Audie Murphy.

Film4.uk.title: Hangman's Knot
Film4.uk.description: (1952) Civil War-era Western. A unit of Confederate soldiers attack a Union troop to steal gold. Learning that the war is over, they must finish the mission in disguise.

Film4.uk.title: The Blue Lamp
Film4.uk.description: (1950) Gritty noir thriller from Ealing Studios. A rookie PC hunts a vicious killer across blitz-battered London. With Jimmy Hanley, Dirk Bogarde and Jack Warner as PC George Dixon.

Film4.uk.title: Film4 Interview Programmes:...
Film4.uk.description: ...Talking Film: Stars and directors talk about making movies in this compendium of personal and practical reflections. Features Danny Boyle, Amy Schumer, Chiwetel Ejiofor and more.

Film4.uk.title: Hunter Killer
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Nautical action thriller. Gerard Butler stars as an unconventional submarine skipper sent to investigate the torpedoing of a US vessel. With Gary Oldman, Linda Cardellini and Common.

Film4.uk.title: Transporter 2
Film4.uk.description: (2005) Violent action-thriller starring Jason Statham as the tough courier Frank Martin, who's hired to guard a government drugs czar's son. But his mission soon lurches towards disaster.

Film4.uk.title: xXx
Film4.uk.description: (2002) Action thriller starring Vin Diesel as Xander Cage: a thrill-seeking extreme sports enthusiast, stuntman and rebellious athlete-turned-reluctant spy. With Samuel L Jackson.

Film4.uk.title: xXx: The Next Level
Film4.uk.description: (2005) Action thriller sequel with Samuel L Jackson and Ice Cube. There's a new Triple X agent in town and he's up against some shady government business. Violence.

Film4.uk.title: A Lawless Street
Film4.uk.description: (1955) A non-stop romp of a western from director Joseph H Lewis. In the town of Medicine Bend, only Marshal Calem Ware can keep its citizens from falling into complete lawlessness.

Film4.uk.title: The Admirable Crichton
Film4.uk.description: (1957) Comedy. Kenneth More stars as the perfect butler, who assumes command when he, his aristocratic employer (Cecil Parker) and his family and friends are shipwrecked on a desert island.

Film4.uk.title: Gift Horse
Film4.uk.description: (1952) War drama. Trevor Howard plays the captain of an ageing US warship, gifted to the British navy, which is chosen to lead the raid on Saint-Nazaire in 1942. With Richard Attenborough.

Film4.uk.title: Enemy Mine
Film4.uk.description: (1985) Sci-fi adventure starring Dennis Quaid and Louis Gossett Jr. A human and his alien enemy find themselves stranded alone on a hostile planet, where they must work together to survive.

Film4.uk.title: Inglourious Basterds
Film4.uk.description: (2009) Quentin Tarantino's World War II action-adventure. Jewish American soldiers go Nazi-hunting in occupied France. With Brad Pitt, Diane Kruger, Christoph Waltz and Michael Fassbender.
